      {
        "id": "01f13ca3d01418eb86ad5e7b17a3f32d",
        "content": [
          "== SIFT SCORE == \r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "When the user asks for a customer's Sift Score, use the risk_alert_management_tool table. Filter AlertType = 'SiftScore' — the actual numeric score is in the SiftScore column. This alert falls under CategoryName = 'Risk' and TriggerType = 'Recurring'. Use RN = 1 to get the latest sift score alert per customer.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== RISK ALERTS (risk_alert_management_tool) == \r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Contains all compliance/risk alerts. Key columns:\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "AlertType — 61 types including: SiftScore, HighFirstTimeDeposit, RapidWithdrawal, DepositNameConflict, HrcLogin, MultipleAccounts, SuspiciousTradingPattern, RussianIndication, SanctionedAddressWallets, HighRiskLogin, HighDepositShortTerm, HighDepositLongTerm, CreditCardVelocity, WithdrawNameConflict, RiskRelations, KycRelations, LifetimeDeposits, NegativeBalanceCheck\r\n",
          "CategoryName — KYC, Risk, Cashouts, AML, Tax, Trading\r\n",
          "StatusType — Active (open/unresolved), Clear (resolved/cleared), Follow Up (needs follow-up)\r\n",
          "StatusReason / Alert_Status_Reason — reason for alert closure or status\r\n",
          "TriggerType — Recurring or one-time\r\n",
          "RN — row number partitioned per CID+AlertType ordered by CreationDate DESC. Use RN = 1 for the latest alert of a given type\r\n",
          "Assignee — agent assigned to the alert\r\n",
          "ModifiedBy — who last modified the alert\r\n",
          "Comment — agent notes\r\n",
          "Contextual columns (populated depending on AlertType): SiftScore, TelesignScore, AllowedTelesignScore, NameConflictScore, FtdAmount, FtdDate, TotalDeposit, DeviceId, RelatedCids, FundingId, FundingTypeId, RiskClassification, Threshold, NextThreshold, MeansOfPayments, CryptoReceiverAddress, CryptoSenderAddress, CryptoWalletstatus, KYCLevel, KycCountryId, RegulationId, YearlySum, DaysPeriod, TimeFrameInDays\r\n",
          "\"how many alerts\" → count distinct AlertID\r\n",
          "\"open alerts\" → StatusType = 'Active'\r\n",
          "\"closed/cleared alerts\" → StatusType = 'Clear'\r\n",
          "== PLAYER STATUS CHANGES (ops_audit_trail) == \r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "When asked \"who changed player status\" or \"player status history\", filter ActionType = 'ChangePlayerStatus'. The PlayerStatus, PlayerStatusReason, PlayerStatusSubReason columns are pre-extracted from the XML AuditActionParameters.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Key ActionType values: ChangePlayerStatus, SetDocumentStatus, SetVerifiedBy, ChangeContactUserInfoDetails, BackOffice.BlockUser, BackOffice.UnBlockUser, Billing.AmountAdd, Billing.WithdrawToFundingChangePaymentStatus, BackOffice.CustomerEditComment, SendNotification, SendPushNotification\r\n",
          "ManagerName — who performed the action\r\n",
          "ActionDate — DATE column for easy filtering\r\n",
          "ActionTime — full TIMESTAMP\r\n",
          "Note: PlayerStatus/Reason/SubReason are only populated for ChangePlayerStatus actions. For other actions, check AuditActionParameters raw XML.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== CUSTOMER INFO (ops_customer_info) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "IsValidCustomer: 1 = valid, 0 = invalid\r\n",
          "VerificationLevelID: 0 = Unverified, 1 = Level 1, 2 = Level 2, 3 = Level 3 (fully verified/KYC complete)\r\n",
          "PlayerStatus: Active, Suspended, Closed, etc.\r\n",
          "PlayerStatusReason / PlayerStatusSubReason: reason for current status\r\n",
          "IsDepositor: TRUE/FALSE\r\n",
          "HasWallet: 1 = has crypto wallet, 0 = no\r\n",
          "Has_eMoney_Account: 'Yes' / 'No'\r\n",
          "IsFTD: first-time depositor flag\r\n",
          "Equity: Liabilities + Non-Withdrawable Amount (as of previous day)\r\n",
          "Balance: credit balance (as of previous day)\r\n",
          "Age: calculated from BirthDate\r\n",
          "CountryRiskGroupID: risk group of KYC country (1 = highest risk)\r\n",
          "FirstName, MiddleName, LastName: customer name\r\n",
          "Address, ZipCode, BuildingNumber, Email, Phone: contact details\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== LOGINS (ops_customer_logins) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Login events only (ActionTypeID = 14)\r\n",
          "LoginCountry: country from IP\r\n",
          "LoginDate: DATE for easy filtering\r\n",
          "LoginDateTime: full TIMESTAMP\r\n",
          "ProxyType: proxy detected (if any)\r\n",
          "CountryRiskGroupID: risk group of login country (1 = highest risk)\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== DEPOSITS (ops_deposits) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "PaymentStatus = 'Approved' for successful deposits\r\n",
          "Other statuses: Decline, New, Pending, InProcess, Canceled, Refund, Chargeback, DeclineByRRE\r\n",
          "IsFTD: 1 = first-time deposit\r\n",
          "FundingType: payment method (credit card, PayPal, wire, etc.)\r\n",
          "BINCountry / MOPCountry / DepositCountry: country of payment method\r\n",
          "AmountUSD: deposit amount in USD\r\n",
          "Amount: deposit amount in original currency\r\n",
          "ExchangeRate: USD conversion rate\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== WITHDRAWALS (ops_withdrawals) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "CashoutStatus = 'Processed' for completed withdrawals\r\n",
          "Other statuses: Canceled, Pending Review, Payment Sent, Reversed, Failed, RejectedByProvider\r\n",
          "WithdrawType / FundingType: withdrawal method\r\n",
          "Flow: withdrawal flow\r\n",
          "AmountUSD: withdrawal amount in USD\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== POSITIONS & TRADING == \r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "ops_positions_details:\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "BuySell: 'Buy' (long) or 'Sell' (short)\r\n",
          "PositionStatus: 'Open' or 'Closed'\r\n",
          "CloseReason: reason closed (only for closed positions)\r\n",
          "IsReal: 1 = real money, 0 = demo\r\n",
          "Profit: realized P&L (closed), CurrentNetProfit: unrealized P&L (open)\r\n",
          "Leverage, Units, Amount: position sizing\r\n",
          "OpenRate, CloseRate, StopRate, LimitRate: price levels\r\n",
          "ParentPositionID, MirrorID: for copy trading relationships\r\n",
          "ops_trading_summary (pre-aggregated by RealCID + InstrumentID, settled positions only):\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Prefer this table for aggregate stats — avoids scanning billions of rows\r\n",
          "TotalPositions, OpenPositions, ClosedPositions\r\n",
          "NumberOfWins / NumberOfLosses\r\n",
          "TotalProfit, MaxProfit, MinProfit\r\n",
          "AvgProfit, AvgAmount\r\n",
          "FirstTradeDate, LastTradeDate\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== RELATIONS (ops_relations) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "MatchReason values: 'Funding ID' (shared payment method), 'Identical check' (identical identity check), 'Device ID' (shared device), 'Similar First name and Last Name', 'Similar First name', 'Similar Last name'\r\n",
          "RealCID/GCID = primary customer; RelatedRealCID/RelatedGCID = linked customer\r\n",
          "\"who is related to CID X\" → filter RealCID = X\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== KYC ANSWERS (ops_kyc_answers) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "QuestionText / AnswerText: Q&A text\r\n",
          "FreeText: optional free-text\r\n",
          "AnswerDate: submission timestamp\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== DOCUMENT ANALYSIS (documentanalysis) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "One row per document upload (by document_id)\r\n",
          "document_type: POI (Proof of Identity), POA (Proof of Address), SOF (Source of Funds)\r\n",
          "rejection_reason / vendor_reason: rejection details\r\n",
          "classification_comment: review notes\r\n",
          "ev_match_status_name: electronic verification status\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== STS AUDIT (bronze_sts_audit_stsaudit_useroperations) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Session-level user operations\r\n",
          "ClientIp, ClientDeviceId, UserAgent: for device/IP investigation\r\n",
          "ActionType: integer code for the operation\r\n",
          "CreatedAt: timestamp of the operation\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== TABLE JOINS == \r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "All ops_* tables join on RealCID. Other tables use different column names:\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "risk_alert_management_tool.CID = ops_customer_info.RealCID\r\n",
          "documentanalysis.cid = ops_customer_info.RealCID\r\n",
          "bronze_sts_audit_stsaudit_useroperations.RealCid = ops_customer_info.RealCID\r\n",
          "bronze_sts_audit_stsaudit_useroperations.Gcid = ops_customer_info.GCID\r\n",
          "ops_relations: join on RealCID for the primary customer. Do NOT join RelatedRealCID to other tables unless explicitly asked about the related customer's details.\r\n",
          "ops_trading_summary joins to ops_positions_details on both RealCID AND InstrumentID\r\n",
          "Common cross-table patterns:\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\"Customer info with alerts\" → ops_customer_info.RealCID = risk_alert_management_tool.CID\r\n",
          "\"Customer info with documents\" → ops_customer_info.RealCID = documentanalysis.cid\r\n",
          "\"Deposits for customers with open alerts\" → join through RealCID = CID and filter StatusType = 'Active'\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "== DEFAULT FILTERS (apply unless user specifies otherwise) ==\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\"deposits\" without status → default to PaymentStatus = 'Approved'\r\n",
          "\"withdrawals\" without status → default to CashoutStatus = 'Processed'\r\n",
          "\"latest alert\" → use RN = 1\r\n",
          "\"trading stats\" or \"position summary\" → prefer ops_trading_summary over ops_positions_details\r\n",
          "\"real customers\" or \"valid customers\" → IsValidCustomer = 1\r\n",
          "\"verified customers\" or \"KYC complete\" → VerificationLevelID = 3\r\n",
          "== IDENTIFIER COLUMN FORMATTING == \r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "When a user queries by CID, GCID, RealCID, DepositID, or WithdrawID, always CAST these columns as STRING in the final SELECT output (e.g., CAST(CID AS STRING) AS CID).\r\n",
          "These identifier columns should never be displayed as numeric values with commas or decimal points — they must appear as plain text strings.\r\n",
          "This applies to all queries that return these columns in the result set.\r\n",
          "Also applies to: TransactionID, ProviderHolderID, GCID, and any other ID column that users may search by."
        ]
      }
